==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Goura
<hw>Gou"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>One of several species of large, crested ground pigeons of the
genus <gen>Goura</gen>, inhabiting New Guinea and adjacent islands. The
Queen Victoria pigeon (<spn>Goura Victoria</spn>) and the crowned pigeon
(<spn>G. coronata</spn>) are among the best known species.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gourami</ent>⟦br⟧
